&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Applied AI Engineering teams to demonstrate technical capabilities pre-sales and optimize solutions post-sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable your team to have credible technical conversations while maintaining appropriate guardrails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong partnerships across the organization to drive strategic initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and execute on new market opportunities and use cases for Anthropic&#39;s AI solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather and synthesize customer feedback to inform product direction and enhance customer experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and continuously refine the sales methodology by incorporating learnings into playbooks and best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
