&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;15+ years of enterprise sales experience driving adoption of emerging technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of sales leadership experience, ideally 3+ leading teams working with F100 accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience closing 9+ figure deals&lt;/li&gt;
