&lt;li&gt;Experience establishing and scaling sales processes, tools, and methodologies in fast-growing organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical acumen and ability to understand complex AI solutions, with experience enabling teams to have credible technical conversations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of successful partnership with technical teams throughout the customer journey&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to navigate dynamic stakeholder ecosystems and drive cross-functional initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing complex enterprise sales cycles and helping AEs secure strategic deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong operational rigor in pipeline management, forecasting, and sales metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and ability to build relationships across all levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic approach to market analysis combined with tactical excellence in execution&lt;/li&gt;
